document_data.name: Aingst
document_data.mainbody: The '''Aingst''' were a tribe of [[Nar (ethnicity)|Nars]] found in western [[Narfell]].
document_data.Activities: Generally speaking, the Aingst did not mind dealing with others, particularly farmers from [[Damara]], so long as they did not tread within the borders of Narfell.
document_data.Base of Operations: The Aingst made their home in and around the [[Giantspire Mountains]] between the border of Narfell and Damara.
